<html>
<head>
    <style>
        body { font-family: 'Arial', sans-serif; background-color: #0B132B; color: #FFFFFF; line-height: 1.6; padding: 40px; margin: 0; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; background: #1A2235; border-radius: 12px; padding: 40px; border: 1px solid #2e3a59; }
        h1 { color: #0A6BFF; margin-top: 0; }
        p { color: #cbd5e1; }
        .btn { display: inline-block; background-color: #0A6BFF; color: #FFFFFF !important; text-decoration: none; padding: 12px 24px; border-radius: 6px; font-weight: bold; margin-top: 20px; }
        .plans { margin-top: 30px; background: rgba(10, 107, 255, 0.05); border: 1px solid rgba(10, 107, 255, 0.2); padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 40px; font-size: 12px; color: #64748b; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <h1>Welcome to SentinelFlow! 🚀</h1>
        <p>Hi {!Lead.FirstName},</p>
        <p>Thank you for reaching out and showing interest in SentinelFlow — the premier AI-powered incident intelligence platform built natively on Salesforce.</p>
        <p>We see that you are looking to eliminate downtime and automate your incident resolution. A member of our team will be reaching out to you shortly at {!Lead.Company} to get you set up.</p>
        
        <div class="plans">
            <h2 style="color: #fff; font-size: 1.2rem; margin-top:0;">Available Plans Overview</h2>
            <p><strong>Starter:</strong> Perfect for small teams. Monitor up to 5 integrations and 100 incidents/month. ($499/mo)</p>
            <p><strong>Professional:</strong> Unlocks AI Auto-Healing, Custom Feature Flags, and up to 20 integrations. ($1,299/mo)</p>
            <p><strong>Enterprise:</strong> Unlimited scale, Multi-Tenant Isolation, Dedicated Support, and 99.9% Uptime SLA. (Custom Pricing)</p>
        </div>

        <p>If you have any immediate questions, simply reply to this email.</p>
        
        <a href="https://sentinelflow.com/docs" class="btn">Explore the Documentation</a>
        
        <div class="footer">
            &copy; 2026 TomCodeX Inc. All rights reserved.<br>
            Salesforce AgentExchange Partner
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
